resultfile = 'CustomerClustering/tmp/explore.xls' #

data = pd.read_csv(datafile, encoding = 'utf-8') #UTF-8UTF-8
data.head()

explore = data.describe(percentiles = [], include = 'all').T #percentiles1/4T
explore['null'] = len(data)-explore['count'] #describe()

explore = explore[['null', 'max', 'min']]
explore.columns = [u'', u'', u''] #
'''
describe()countuniquetopfreqmeanstdmin50%max'''

explore.to_excel(resultfile) #

数据清洗，过滤掉不符合规则的数据¶

In [26]:
#-*- coding: utf-8 -*-
import pandas as pd
datafile= 'CustomerClustering/data/air_data.csv' #,
cleanedfile = 'CustomerClustering/tmp/air_data_cleaned.csv' #

data = pd.read_csv(datafile,encoding='utf-8') #UTF-8UTF-8
print (" ", len(data))

data = data[data['SUM_YR_1'].notnull() & data['SUM_YR_2'].notnull()] #

#0
index1 = data['SUM_YR_1'] != 0
index2 = data['SUM_YR_2'] != 0
index3 = (data['SEG_KM_SUM'] == 0) & (data['avg_discount'] == 0) #
data = data[index1 | index2 | index3] #


# LRFMC6
data = data[['FFP_DATE','LAST_TO_END','FLIGHT_COUNT','SEG_KM_SUM','LOAD_TIME','avg_discount']]
data.to_csv(cleanedfile,encoding='utf-8',index=False) #
print (" ", len(data))

数据可视化¶

In [203]:
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns#

datafile= 'CustomerClustering/data/air_data.csv'
data = pd.read_csv(datafile,encoding='utf-8')
data = data[data['SUM_YR_1'].notnull() & data['SUM_YR_2'].notnull()]
index1 = data['SUM_YR_1'] != 0
index2 = data['SUM_YR_2'] != 0
index3 = (data['SEG_KM_SUM'] == 0) & (data['avg_discount'] == 0)
data = data[index1 | index2 | index3]

def feature_box(feature, data):#
    print(data[feature].describe())
    data[feature].plot.box(title = feature)
    plt.grid(linestyle="--", alpha=0.3)
    plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif']=['SimHei','Times New Roman'] # 
    plt.show()

def feature_bar(feature, data):#
    print(data[feature].describe())
    feat_data = data[feature].value_counts()
    sns.barplot(feat_data.index.values, feat_data.values)
    plt.grid(linestyle="--", alpha=0.3)
    plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif']=['SimHei','Times New Roman'] # 
    plt.show()

标准差标准化¶

In [27]:
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

datafile= 'CustomerClustering/data/air_data_cleaned.csv' #,
normdfile = 'CustomerClustering/data/air_data_normd.csv' #
#UTF-8UTF-8
data = pd.read_csv(datafile,encoding='utf-8')
data[u'LOAD_TIME'] = pd.to_datetime(data[u'LOAD_TIME'])
data[u'FFP_DATE'] = pd.to_datetime(data[u'FFP_DATE'])
#days
data['L'] = (data[u'LOAD_TIME'] - data[u'FFP_DATE']) / np.timedelta64(1, 'M')
data['R'] = data['LAST_TO_END']
data['F'] = data['FLIGHT_COUNT']
data['M'] = data['SEG_KM_SUM']
data['C'] = data['avg_discount']
#LRFMC5
data = data[['L','R','F','M','C']]
#z-score
data = (data - data.mean(axis = 0)) / (data.std(axis = 0))
data.columns = ['Z'+i for i in data.columns] #
data.to_csv(normdfile,encoding='utf-8',index=False) #
data.head()
